The '''red-fronted barbet''' ('''''Tricholaema diademata''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the [[Lybiidae]] family.
It is found in [[Ethiopia]], [[Kenya]], [[South Sudan]], [[Tanzania]], and [[Uganda]].

